OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FA teenager has denied "gang raping" a
OL,8,Fgirl in bushes near a tram stop,
OL,9,Ftelling a jury he engaged in "100
OL,10,Fpercent" consensual sexual activity
OL,11,Fwith her.
OL,13,FThree boys - who cannot be named
OL,14,Fbecause of their ages - are alleged to
OL,15,Fhave raped the girl when they were 12,
OL,16,F13 and 14.
OL,18,FThe teenage girl, who also cannot be
OL,19,Fnamed, was allegedly attacked just off
OL,20,Fa footpath near the Newbold tram stop
OL,21,Fin Rochdale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
