PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FThe jury was previously told the boys
OL,8,F"took it in turns and swapped
OL,9,Fpositions" during the incident in
OL,10,FFebruary 2024.
OL,12,FThe eldest defendant, now aged 16,
OL,13,Fgave evidence in the case on Tuesday
OL,14,F10 March, stating that on the day of
OL,15,Fthe incident he had been in Rochdale
OL,16,Ftown centre with his two co-accused
OL,17,Fand one other boy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FHe said they had been "running around,
OL,8,Fjoking around town" before they
OL,9,Fencountered some other youngsters at
OL,10,Fthe tram stop.
OL,12,FAsked if he recognised the alleged
OL,13,Fvictim and her friend he said he had
OL,14,F"more than likely probably seen them"
OL,15,Fbefore, but that he didn't know them.
OL,17,FThey boarded the same tram and the boy
OL,18,Fsaid that during the "eight-to-nine-
OL,19,Fminute" journey to Newbold, there was
OL,20,F"talking and flirting".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FHe said there was then conversation
OL,8,Fabout "who fancied who" and the
OL,9,Falleged victim's friend had said that
OL,10,Fthe alleged victim "liked" his co-
OL,11,Fdefendant.
OL,13,FHe said: "I asked (the alleged victim)
OL,14,Fdid she like me and she said yes." He
OL,15,Fsaid there was then "conversation
OL,16,Fabout s******g".
OL,26,@uD@SpmuD@fpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FHe said they "all agreed" to go the
OL,8,Fbushes and that the alleged victim
OL,9,F"suggested we go and get some condoms"
OL,10,Fbut that they had told her they didn't
OL,11,Fhave any money and that she said it
OL,12,Fwas "okay to do it without".
OL,14,FThe now-16-year-old told the court the
OL,15,Falleged victim "voluntarily walked
OL,16,Finto the bushes" and "she went first".
OL,17,FHe said whilst inside the bushes she
OL,18,Fbegan performing a sex act on his co-
OL,19,Fdefendant before then doing the same
OL,20,Fto him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FWhen asked by his barrister Rachel
OL,8,FShenton if the alleged victim did or
OL,9,Fsaid anything to suggest she wasn't
OL,10,Fagreeing, the defendant said "it was
OL,11,F100 percent willingly".
OL,13,FThe boy said he then attempted to have
OL,14,Fintercourse with her. Ms Shenton then
OL,15,Fasked: "Would it be fair to say you
OL,16,Fwere not very successful at that?".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FThe defendant told the court "yes",
OL,8,Fstating "it was my first time", before
OL,9,Fstating that he would not have done
OL,10,Fany of these actions if he felt she
OL,11,Fwas not consenting.
OL,13,FHe said he went home and ate a
OL,14,Fsandwich before going back out. He
OL,15,Fsaid: "If I thought I had committed an
OL,16,Foffence I don't think I would have
OL,17,Fgone back to the town."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FHe said he asked his co-defendant to
OL,8,Fsend him a Snapchat video the court
OL,9,Fhas heard was filmed during the
OL,10,Fincident. "Did you believe that was a
OL,11,Fvideo of the rape of the girl?" Ms
OL,12,FShenton asked him. "No," he replied.
OL,14,FAsked by Ms Shenton how he felt
OL,15,Fafterwards about the fact he had had
OL,16,Fhis "first sexual encounter" and had
OL,17,F"lost his virginity" he said: "I was
OL,18,Fhappy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FThe boy said he now feels ashamed
OL,8,Fabout the incident, telling the court
OL,9,F"Because I am getting blamed for
OL,10,Fsomething I didn't do".
OL,12,FHe said: "I didn't do anything wrong,
OL,13,FI don't know why I'm in this situation
OL,14,Fto be honest."
OL,16,FThe boy said he left school early and
OL,17,Fnever received any sex education,
OL,18,Fhowever, he said that he had been
OL,19,F"brought up to be respectful" to women.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FWhen asked if he gang raped the
OL,8,Falleged victim, or if that is
OL,9,Fsomething he would ever do, the boy
OL,10,Fsaid no.
OL,12,FUnder cross-examination from
OL,13,Fprosecutor Kim Whittlestone, the boy
OL,14,Fsaid that whilst on the tram, he had
OL,15,Fasked the alleged victim if she wanted
OL,16,Fto "s**g" him and that she had said
OL,17,F"yes."
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FProsecutor Whittlestone asked him:
OL,8,F"Did she appear to want to be in your
OL,9,Fcompany?" to which the boy replied
OL,10,F"yes".
OL,12,FWhittlestone continued: "Did you think
OL,13,Fit it was slightly odd you were going
OL,14,Fto have sex with her in the bushes?"
OL,15,F"No" he replied.
OL,17,FWhen asked if he thought this was odd
OL,18,Ffor his first time, the defendant
OL,19,Fsaid: "I wouldn't think it was odd if
OL,20,Fshe agreed to do it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FThe boy said he was "not clear" about
OL,8,Fthe precise events in the bushes but
OL,9,Fdenied that the girl was "being told
OL,10,Fwhat to do."
OL,12,F"What did you think about it being
OL,13,Frecorded?" Ms Whittlestone asked him.
OL,14,F"I didn't really think about that," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe said the footage was shared with
OL,18,Fhim but said he did not share it with
OL,19,Fanyone else.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773252370
OL,3,CBoy accused of 'gang rape' says he
OL,4,Cfelt 'happy' after 'consensual'
OL,5,Cencounter
OL,7,FPreviously, Ms Whittlestone said the
OL,8,Fnow 14-year-old has been found unfit
OL,9,Fto stand trial. She said the jury
OL,10,Fwould be asked to find "whether he did
OL,11,Fthe act" and whether he "encouraged"
OL,12,Fit to happen without the girl's
OL,13,Fconsent.
OL,15,FThe indictment contains five counts of
OL,16,Frape. Three counts relate specifically
OL,17,Fto each boy, while two are charged as
OL,18,F"joint enterprise", jurors were told.
OL,19,FEach boy denies the charges they face.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
